{ With this it might become possible to send }
{ data out over the game controller port }

gcl0x

$800 p= {Heartbeat}
  1+ q=
\SYS_SendSerial_vX_80 \sysFn=

[do
 {Delay loop}
  0 [do p. 1+ if<>0loop]

  [def 1#  0#  2#  1# 2# ] \sysArgs0=
  5 \sysArgs2.
  5 \sysArgs3.

  63 q. {Indicate sending}

  80!

  32 q.

loop]

